{"tid":1333292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何令屋企人了解多少少今次嘅抗爭","createTime":"2019-07-19T15:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:48.000Z","uid":162347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57ecd59de409c512a4a981e23973ee0737db40b5","tid":1333292,"uid":162347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴/絲打，有無啲咩片or文章令屋企人快速了解我哋做緊嘅嘢！因為岩岩喺到傾計，我啊媽就話佢係撐警察，我都心平氣和咁問佢點解，佢就話啲示威者咬斷警察手指好暴力！我就問佢TVB同你講架？佢話緊係啦！新聞黎架嘛！跟著就爭論咗一段時間，佢就同我講，其實佢知嘅都唔多，淨係覺得警察係正義，維持治安！都想我同佢講，解釋俾佢聽，我就打算send啲片or文章俾佢睇下。或者你哋會唔會有啲咩意見，俾啲而家仲未係好了解嘅人有一個詳細少少嘅懶人包！感謝！！！"},{"pid":"cbacc886fa3a5bde81addb9527abdc88c3cf2aca","tid":1333292,"uid":162347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66ca8c87e1e2da330005e15fb1a48b945d1238aa","tid":1333292,"uid":162347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:43:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dcbf473c59004609c2aa38fd4da6fa7ecdc08d06","tid":1333292,"uid":162347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"892ab4a630a0493da4e53ad7dbda8feab3ae4485","tid":1333292,"uid":162347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"480b5b4db90afd56bdfb328c25fe2e499be22a88","tid":1333292,"uid":162347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}